data.description: Well-located, 2 BD/1 BA, home! Just mins. to dwtn. Sevierville, Pigeon Forge, & much more. Ideal as a permanent or 2nd home -great location, just minutes to nearby shopping, schools, LeConte Medical Center, Dollywood, & much more. Includes an attached 1-car garage, a rear open patio/porch.  Living room area w/a F/P, an open dining area. Full kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances and 1/2 bath downstairs. Both bedrooms located on the 2nd floor with a shared jack and jill bathroom, each room have their own toilets, but shared tub/shower. Lots of potential in a great location. Includes City-maintained services, including water, sewer, & more. Note* the restrictions refer to the property as a townhome the tax records refer to the property as a condo.
